name: O. D. E. Subscription "Blue Sky"
description: "Blue Sky" for business: an exclusive area for brands where it is possible to publish 6 pictures (for a single product or 6 different products) accompanied by a text of presentation of the design project or information and contacts about the company.

name: O. D. E. Subscription "Rose"
description: "Rose" for designer and Design Studios: an exclusive area for designers ans their activity, where it is possible to publish 6 pictures (for a single product or 6 different products) accompanied by a text of presentation of the design project or information and contacts about the company.

name: O. D. E. Subscription "Orange"
description:
"Orange" for business: the second option for brands. In this area is possible to publish 6 pictures (for a single product or 6 different products) accompanied by a text of presentation of the design project or information and contacts about the company.
This subscription is valid to be on O. D. E. during the opening days of multiple events, chosen according to the list / calendar "Around the World", or for a continuous period of not more than 90 days. To subscribe to a period longer than this, please chose "Abbonamento E"

name: O. D. E. Subscription "Mint"
description:
"Mint" for fresh design: the second option for Designer and Design Studios. In this area is possible to publish 6 pictures (for a single product or 6 different products) accompanied by a text of presentation of the design project or information and contacts about designers ad Studios.
This subscription is valid to be on O. D. E. during the opening days of multiple events, chosen according to the list / calendar "Around the World", or for a continuous period of not more than 90 days. To subscribe to a period longer than this, please chose "Subscription Gold"
